---
import Layout from "../layouts/Default.astro";
import DoubleCta from "../components/DoubleCta.astro";
const title = "Home";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <div class="hero is-fullheight is-center has-top-bg">
    <img class="top-bg-alt" src="/img/bg/top-bg-alt.svg" alt="" />

    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="columns is-vcentered mt-6">
          <div class="column">
            <h1 class="title is-1 is-bold">Building the future of Africa</h1>
            <p
              class="subtitle is-5 mx-auto max-w-5 b-centered-tablet-p text-medium"
            >
              We seek to invest in and support Africa's most promising
              technology startups
            </p>
            <div class="buttons">
              <a class="button is-primary is-medium is-raised">Discover</a>
              <a class="button is-primary is-outlined is-medium">Free Trial</a>
            </div>
            <img
              class="hero-image-center mx-auto py-4 inverted-filter"
              src="/img/illustrations/skyline.svg"
              alt="Hero image"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="has-text-centered pb-6">
        <span class="tag is-primary is-curved is-outlined is-thick mb-2"
          >Strong Ideals </span
        >
        <h2 class="title is-3">Impact Driven</h2>
        <p class="subtitle is-5 text-medium">
          Focused on helping the marginalised
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-block-v1">
        <div
          class="columns is-multiline b-columns-half-tablet-p has-text-centered"
        >
          <!-- Feature -->
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div class="py-4">
              <i
                class="iconify rem-200 text-primary"
                data-icon="fa6-solid:microchip"></i>
              <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Deeply Tech</h4>
              <p class="pt-2 mx-auto max-w-3 text-medium rem-95">
                We partner with startups where technology preferably drives the
                business model, not just supports it.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Feature -->
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div class="py-4">
              <i
                class="iconify rem-200 text-primary"
                data-icon="fluent:people-team-32-regular"></i>
              <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Team centric</h4>
              <p class="pt-2 mx-auto max-w-3 text-medium rem-95">
                We focus on people and teams, partnering with founders to drive
                success, not just providing funding.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Feature -->
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div class="py-4">
              <i class="iconify rem-200 text-primary" data-icon="icons8:idea"
              ></i>
              <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Fresh Perspectives</h4>
              <p class="pt-2 mx-auto max-w-3 text-medium rem-95">
                We seek out startups that not only innovate, but also drive
                positive change in communities they serve.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Feature -->
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div class="py-4">
              <i
                class="iconify rem-200 text-primary"
                data-icon="carbon:crop-growth"></i>
              <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Traction</h4>
              <p class="pt-2 mx-auto max-w-3 text-medium rem-95">
                We support startups demonstrating early success, proven demand,
                and a scalable business model.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Feature -->
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div class="py-4">
              <i
                class="iconify rem-200 text-primary"
                data-icon="ph:rocket-duotone"></i>
              <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Propellant</h4>
              <p class="pt-2 mx-auto max-w-3 text-medium rem-95">
                We can guide startups through larger funding rounds and connect
                them with later stage investors.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Feature -->
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div class="py-4">
              <i
                class="iconify rem-200 text-primary"
                data-icon="la:globe-africa"></i>
              <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Love Africa</h4>
              <p class="pt-2 mx-auto max-w-3 text-medium rem-95">
                We are agnostic of geography but get really excited about
                startups with an Africa-centric focus.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section has-pseudo-lines">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="py-6">
        <div class="columns is-vcentered b-centered-tablet-p">
          <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
            <span class="is-block is-uppercase mb-2 text-primary"
              >Partnering you</span
            >
            <h3 class="title is-3 is-narrow max-w-3 small:mx-auto">
              Support all the way
            </h3>
            <p class="py-2 max-w-4 text-medium mb-4 small:mx-auto">
              Our tech-savvy investors give our portfolio companies the
              resources and support they need to level up their pursuit.
            </p>
            <ul class="pl-4 small:hidden">
              <li class="is-flex is-align-items-center py-2">
                <i class="iconify text-primary rem-125" data-icon="lucide:check"
                ></i>
                <div class="ml-2">
                  <p class="small:max-w-2 text-medium">
                    Experienced & Commercial
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="is-flex is-align-items-center py-2">
                <i class="iconify text-primary rem-125" data-icon="lucide:check"
                ></i>
                <div class="ml-2">
                  <p class="small:max-w-2 text-medium">Deeply Technical</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="is-flex is-align-items-center py-2">
                <i class="iconify text-primary rem-125" data-icon="lucide:check"
                ></i>
                <div class="ml-2">
                  <p class="small:max-w-2 text-medium">Connected</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-6">
            <img
              class="light-image-block"
              src="/img/vectors/good-team.svg"
              alt=""
            />
            <img
              class="dark-image-block"
              src="/img/vectors/good-team.svg"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section has-pseudo-lines">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="has-text-centered py-12">
        <span class="tag is-primary is-curved is-outlined is-thick mb-2"
          >Who we are</span
        >
        <h2 class="title is-3">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="subtitle is-5 text-medium">
          We weren't always amongst the top players
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="py-12">
        <div class="columns is-vcentered">
          <div class="column is-6 is-relative is-centered-portrait">
            <div class="video-player-container is-square">
              <video
                id="hero-player"
                class="video-player"
                playsinline
                controls
                poster="/img/video/poster-1c.jpg"
              >
                <source src="/img/video/hands.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                <source src="/img/video/hands.webm" type="video/webm" />
              </video>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
            <h2 class="title is-3 small:text-centered">Our Values</h2>

            <div
              class="columns is-multiline small:max-w-5 small:mx-auto small:px-8"
            >
              <div class="column is-6">
                <div class="py-2 medium:py-4">
                  <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Commitment</h4>
                  <p class="pt-2 max-w-3 text-medium rem-90">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed
                    videbimus.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-6">
                <div class="py-2 medium:py-4">
                  <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Collaboration</h4>
                  <p class="pt-2 max-w-3 text-medium rem-90">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed
                    videbimus.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-6">
                <div class="py-2 medium:py-4">
                  <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Diversity</h4>
                  <p class="pt-2 max-w-3 text-medium rem-90">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed
                    videbimus.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-6">
                <div class="py-2 medium:py-4">
                  <h4 class="title is-6 is-narrow">Remote Work</h4>
                  <p class="pt-2 max-w-3 text-medium rem-90">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed
                    videbimus.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section is-minimal has-pseudo-lines">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pt-12 pb-4 mx-auto max-w-8">
        <div class="has-text-centered mb-8">
          <span class="tag is-primary is-curved is-outlined is-thick mb-2"
            >Multipurpose</span
          >
          <h2 class="title is-3">Fit for any purpose</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="columns">
          <div class="column is-6">
            <p
              class="text-medium small:text-centered small:mx-auto small:max-w-5"
            >
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Idem
              iste, inquam, de voluptate quid sentit? Hanc quoque iucunditatem,
              si vis, transfer in animum; Erat enim Polemonis. Apparet statim,
              quae sint officia, quae actiones. Ita prorsus, inquam.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-6">
            <p
              class="text-medium small:text-centered small:mx-auto small:max-w-5"
            >
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Idem
              iste, inquam, de voluptate quid sentit? Hanc quoque iucunditatem,
              si vis, transfer in animum; Erat enim Polemonis. Apparet statim,
              quae sint officia, quae actiones. Ita prorsus, inquam.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-block-v8 pb-12">
          <div class="columns is-multiline">
            <div class="column is-12">
              <div class="block mb-4 has-text-centered mx-auto max-w-8">
                <div class="mx-auto max-w-7">
                  <div class="video-player-container is-16by9">
                    <video
                      id="hero-player"
                      class="video-player"
                      playsinline
                      controls
                      poster="/img/video/poster-1a.jpg"
                    >
                      <source src="/img/video/hands.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                      <source src="/img/video/hands.webm" type="video/webm" />
                    </video>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="columns b-columns-third-tablet-p has-text-left mt-4"
                >
                  <!-- Feature -->
                  <div class="column is-4 has-text-centered">
                    <div
                      class="mx-auto is-44x44 is-flex is-justify-content-center is-align-items-center is-circle bg-grey"
                    >
                      <i
                        class="iconify rem-175 text-primary"
                        data-icon="ph:sticker-duotone"></i>
